      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.classes.0tC4GBpJ0S17VR6a]{Precog}</p>\n<p>You can execute precisely timed moves that help you and others dodge incoming attacks. As a reaction when an attack is declared but before the result is known, you can use a paradox to grant an ally an insight bonus to AC until the end of your next turn. This bonus is equal to the paradox result or a maximum bonus of +2, whichever is lower. The maximum bonus increases to +3 at 7th level, +4 at 13th level, and +5 at 18th level.</p>"
